e, Candidate\u202fC best satisfies the essential safety, decision\u2011making, and crew\u2011interaction requirements for a long\u2011distance pilot, despite the noted communication and development concerns.\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_1\", \"vote\": \"Candidate C\"}"}
